_sText:
This is the first release of my new css map de_cityfever_beta (I know, it is still beta and it contains a lot of bugs). There are over 2 Months and 200 hours of work to get this map done. Hopefully the map is the work worth.


Some information:
Made for the German eSports magazine eFever.
Standard Half-Life 2 Setting (City/Urban) without the Combine
de_ (Bomb/Defuse) Map
32MB Smile
2 Bombspots
2 Teams
